e-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-927369ecad8da2459 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:34px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:44px;\"}'  style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#222222;margin-bottom:30px;\">The way to get started is to quit talking and begin doing!<\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text]<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Klimacontra is a pioneering company in the HVAC market, specializing in a wide range of products. Our manufacturing range of products include air movement solutions, fire &amp; smoke management products, and various HVAC accessories. These range from grilles, diffusers, louvers, to axial and centrifugal fans. Additionally, we provide fire\/smoke dampers, fire-resistant materials, and more. Our products are rigorously tested and certified, meeting the highest standards such as EN, CE, UL, and ISO.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Customer-Centric Approach<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">At Klimacontra, customer satisfaction is paramount. We are committed to meeting the specific needs of our customers&#8217; projects by providing high-quality products at affordable prices. Our presence in Lebanon, Cyprus, Africa and Saudi Arabia enables us to efficiently supply the HVAC sector across the globe.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Vision and Scope<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Our ambition is to become a leading supplier in the MEP sector and contribute significantly to the development of engineering companies in the world. We cater to a diverse range of projects, including Banks, Data Centers, Oil &amp; Gas facilities, Metro stations, and more. Our client portfolio extends to Commercial, Residential, Hospital sectors, Tunnels, Hotels, High-rises, Towers, and Pharmaceutical projects.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Product Range and Innovation<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">We offer CE-marked products suitable for all types of projects. Our extensive product line includes a full range of Fans, Air Outlets, Heat Recovery Units, European Fire Dampers, and CE Marked Air Curtains. Moreover, we provide HEPA and aluminum filters, Special polymer Diffusers, UL Duct heaters, Tunnel and Subway System Ventilation, and Thermal Insulation, Jacketing and Fastening solutions, all at competitive prices. Klimacontra is an AMCA member, and has a wide range of tested products according to Ashrae, EN, Standards.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Commitment to Research and Development<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Our dedicated R&amp;D team continuously works on enhancing and expanding the KLIMACONTRA product range. This effort ensures we can always meet and exceed our clients&#8217; evolving needs and demands.<\/span>[\/vc_column_text]<style type=\"text\/css\" data-type=\"the7_shortcodes-inline-css\">.dt-shortcode-soc-icons.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f a {\n  margin-right: 4px;\n}\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f {\n  margin-right: 4px;\n}\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f:last-child {\n  margin-right: 0;\n}\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f:before,\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f:after {\n  padding: inherit;\n}\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f.dt-icon-border-on:before {\n  border:  solid ;\n}\n.dt-shortcode-soc-icons a.soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f.dt-icon-hover-border-on:after {\n  border:  solid ;\n}\n<\/style><div class=\"dt-shortcode-soc-icons  soc-icons-6d3d70cdad80c3022dac88b2b035272f soc-icons-center \" ><\/div>[\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1718694109553{padding-top: 85px !important;padding